India Facing Difficult Inflationary Situation, Adviser Basu Says

-- B y   T u s h a r   D h a r a
-- 
2011-09-16T08:20:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/india-facing-difficult-inflationary-situation-adviser-basu-says.html
India  is facing a “difficult
inflationary situation,” as the central bank tries to balance
between economic growth and prices, Kaushik Basu, the chief
economic adviser in the finance ministry, told reporters in  New
Delhi  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
